      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZINFANDEL TREV (1) hit the ground running and set it up early clocking 30.77 with a 7 length win at this track over 530m. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Will go close again if runs up to latest. WHITE HAWKE (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (31.26) last time in a Grade 6 at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in four starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. CANYA CONCORDE (2) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (36.15) in a Grade 6/MDN at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Must be included in calculations. ADHANA HENRY (6) is worth including.",
